We calculated the selection pressures acting on genes by comparing non-synonymous substitution per non-synonymous site (dN) to the synonymous substitutions per synonymous site (dS). This ratio of the number of non-synonymous substitutions per non-synonymous site to the number of synonymous substitutions per synonymous site (dN/dS) was calculated using the formula \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
